quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  100,10,"and whatever is on [people´s] minds is checked up on"
  100,11,their Lord will be Informed about them on that day
  101,1,"The stunning [blow]"
  101,2,What is a disaster
  101,3,"What will make you realize something is going to stun [you]"
  101,4,Someday mankind will act like scattered moths
  101,5,and the mountains seem like tufts of yarn
  101,6,So anyone whose scales are weighted down
  101,7,"[will land] in pleasant living"
  101,8,while whoever´s scales are light
  101,9,will have a Pit to mother him
  101,10,What will make you realize what this will be like
  101,11,Scorching fire
  102,1,Competition has distracted you
  102,2,until you visit graveyards
  102,3,Nevertheless you soon will know
  102,4,"once more, you soon shall know"
  102,5,"Of course, if you realized with absolute certainty"
  102,6,how you will (all) see Hades
  102,7,"then you would see it with the [very] eye of certainty"
  102,8,next you will be questioned concerning bliss on that day